			<div id="banner-copy-position">
            	<p class="banner-text">Manufacturer of Hall Tilt-Pour Permanent Mold Casting Machines<br>(Gravity Die Casting Machines) &amp; Foundry Systems</p>
            </div>
            
			<div id="welcome-copy-position">
				<p class="welcome-page-copy">CMH produces the HALL line of foundry equipment with special emphasis on aluminum<a href="traditional_tilting_machines/index.htm"> tilt pour</a> gravity die casting machines. In 2004 we purchased the engineering to the Stahl line of casting equipment and now offer parts/equipment to meet your needs. CMH offers a full line of <a href="autocast/index.htm">Autocast</a> die casting machines,<a href="casting_catchers/index.htm"> casting catchers</a>, <a href="rotary_style_machines/index.htm">rotary tables</a>, peripheral work cell support equipment, <a href="services.htm">robotics</a> and <a href="services.htm">automation equipment</a> designed around the tilt pour principle.  </p>
